></mjx-c></mjx-mo><mjx-mn class=3D"mjx-n" space=3D"4"><mjx-c class=3D"mjx-c=
32"></mjx-c><mjx-c class=3D"mjx-c34"></mjx-c></mjx-mn></mjx-math><mjx-assis=
tive-mml unselectable=3D"on" display=3D"inline"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w=
3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>6</mn><mo>=C3=97</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=3D</mo><mn>=
24</mn></math></mjx-assistive-mml></mjx-container></p>



<p class=3D"eplus-wrapper">Thus, quotient <mjx-container class=3D"MathJax C=
txtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"CHTML" tabindex=3D"0" ctxtmenu_counter=3D"1" sty=
le=3D"font-size: 121.3%; position: relative;"><mjx-math class=3D"MJX-TEX" a=
ria-hidden=3D"true"><mjx-mo class=3D"mjx-n"><mjx-c class=3D"mjx-c3D"></mjx-=
c></mjx-mo><mjx-mn class=3D"mjx-n" space=3D"4"><mjx-c class=3D"mjx-c34"></m=
jx-c></mjx-mn></mjx-math><mjx-assistive-mml unselectable=3D"on" display=3D"=
inline"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=3D</mo><mn>=
4</mn></math></mjx-assistive-mml></mjx-container> and we are left with the =
remainder of 1.</p>



<figure class=3D"wp-block-image size-full eplus-wrapper"><img fetchpriority=
