der-2.png" alt=3D"25 divided by 6 long division showing parts of division" =
class=3D"wp-image-27420" title=3D"25 divided by 6 long division showing par=
ts of division"></figure>



<p class=3D"eplus-wrapper">We can write this as <mjx-container class=3D"Mat=
