<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading eplus-wrapper" id=3D"10-facts-about-remainder=
">Facts about Remainder</h2>



<ul class=3D"eplus-wrapper wp-block-list">
<li class=3D"eplus-wrapper">When one number divides another number complete=
ly, the remainder is 0 and the division is called complete division.</li>
</ul>



<ul class=3D"eplus-wrapper wp-block-list">
<li class=3D"eplus-wrapper">The word remainder comes from the Latin word =
=E2=80=9Cremanere,=E2=80=9D which means =E2=80=9Cto remain.=E2=80=9D</li>
</ul>



